{"tid":1151042,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"點解要反返送中？","createTime":"2019-05-12T09:46:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-12T10:41:44.000Z","uid":216528,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1237ad3a72446fd04809df647c13cc06f8a2a625","tid":1151042,"uid":216528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T09:46:10.000Z","msg":"劇本早己寫好，就係中國實挽燃完<br />\n<br />\n香港係中國洗黑錢既地方,西方國家應該會收埋我哋皮<br />\n<br />\n反正都係死，抱住啲供緊樓、啱先買完樓走資既大陸閪、同埋啲無創力只會收租既垃圾地主一齊做loser, 咁就好挽了<br />\n<br />\n嘻嘻嘻，好想快啲收啲大陸佬皮<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com/amp/s/www.ntdtv.com/b5/2019/05/08/a102573973.html/amp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Famp%2Fs%2Fwww.ntdtv.com%2Fb5%2F2019%2F05%2F08%2Fa102573973.html%2Famp&d=gf59OkzbMHBVvJ2bZZ4HaseYC5A6rl8%2B6t9FBevN87M%3D&h=238025b9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/amp/s/www.ntdtv.com/b5/2019/05/08/a102573973.html/amp</a><br />\n<br />\n&quot;自去年開始糧食大清查之後，中國各地糧庫火災不斷，糧食部門官員集體落馬的消息也不絕於耳。外界猜測，<span style=\"color: red;\">糧庫火災基本都是為掩蓋糧食虧空。＂</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com/amp/s/m.ltn.com.tw/amp/news/world/breakingnews/2785889\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Famp%2Fs%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Famp%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2785889&d=gf59OkzbMHBVvJ2bZZ4HaseYC5A6rl8%2B6t9FBevN87M%3D&h=27d68513\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/amp/s/m.ltn.com.tw/amp/news/world/breakingnews/2785889</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">&quot;秋行軍蟲對農作物威脅極大，目前尚無大規模撲殺辦法。＂</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://cn.nytimes.com/china/20190423/china-pigs-african-swine-fever/zh-hant/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcn.nytimes.com%2Fchina%2F20190423%2Fchina-pigs-african-swine-fever%2Fzh-hant%2F&d=gf59OkzbMHBVvJ2bZZ4HaseYC5A6rl8%2B6t9FBevN87M%3D&h=1e773573\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://cn.nytimes.com/china/20190423/china-pigs-african-swine-fever/zh-hant/</a><br />\n<br />\n＂但疫情實際上可能要更嚴峻。一些農民在接受採訪時表示，<span style=\"color: red;\">沒有向當地政府報告他們的牲口可能受到感染。還有人稱，官員沒有對上報的疫情給予迅速回應。＂</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><a href=\"https://youtu.be/BETn7zmm2u4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FBETn7zmm2u4&d=gf59OkzbMHBVvJ2bZZ4HaseYC5A6rl8%2B6t9FBevN87M%3D&h=1df5b4a6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/BETn7zmm2u4</a><br />\n&quot;fake news!中國銀行美金用完唔敢上報&quot;</span><br />\n<br />\n中國人，中國香港人都係人渣。美國及西方文明社會快啲處決呢啲地球既害蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b86ae6087a8318ae3b98e06c07c5f86ca439390","tid":1151042,"uid":216528,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T09:49:42.000Z","msg":"地球己鎖定支那人係害蟲,所有天災人禍將會集中於中國"},{"pid":"982ccc111839726e6d1ff51971efd87d4be20283","tid":1151042,"uid":2419,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T09:51:56.000Z","msg":"露撚晒底啦 返去再培訓啦"},{"pid":"1b4819c077a31cd9492280c3ddb6c4b978c63114","tid":1151042,"uid":216528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T09:54:01.000Z","msg":"嘻嘻嘻，殺哂所有支那,同埋支那香港人"},{"pid":"859b67c1a7cbea2c797c2a24723cef711ac366c8","tid":1151042,"uid":216528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"982ccc111839726e6d1ff51971efd87d4be20283","tid":1151042,"uid":2419,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T09:51:56.000Z","msg":"露撚晒底啦 返去再培訓啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T09:55:09.000Z","msg":"支那人，準備好日日食樹皮未呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fad38cbd466b46195485b90397e563114b77c123","tid":1151042,"uid":50658,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T09:57:11.000Z","msg":"挽你老母咩"},{"pid":"b5aa7294bfad0edcf4afaef5e261694586400556","tid":1151042,"uid":90820,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T09:57:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;